help_title="Learn to walk before you run."

help_short="This level will teach you the basic movement commands."
help_long="vim has over 40 movement commands. This may seem like a lot, but they are logically paired and well spread out over the keyboard. The enormous variety of movement commands allows you, once you know them, to move extremely quickly within a document.\nThe movement commands have been split into two bashcraft levels. This level covers basic movements."

